dct_description_sm: Map shows county, city and borough boundaries; 4 classes of roads; railroads; postal zones and numbers; places of worship; and other features. Inset of: Christchurch inner city, scale 1:12,500. "Compiled: July 1987." New Zealand map grid. Indexes on verso.
dct_creator_sm: New Zealand. Department of Survey and Land Information
dct_publisher_sm: Wellington, N.Z. : Dept. of Survey and Land Information, 1987.
